{"tid":2364741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中原地產：積累購買力突大爆發！嘉湖山莊升值88%！！","createTime":"2021-01-13T08:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T08:41:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"316ff3db700adbc38c395bae0e1f02ade6613fb1","tid":2364741,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"中原葉浩麟表示，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>疫情轉趨緩和下，積累的購買力紛紛加快入市</strong></span>，天水圍嘉湖山莊本月成交暢旺，已錄得23宗成交，其中景湖居7座低層F室兩房戶，以485萬港元成交。原業主於1997年5月以258萬元買入單位，持貨近24年帳面獲利227萬元，單位期內升值約88%。該單位實用面積約442方呎，成交呎價約10,973元，屬市場價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210113/bkn-20210113154638289-0113_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210113%2Fbkn-20210113154638289-0113_00842_001.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0f62f906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210113/bkn-20210113154638289-0113_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9217f42d8f8b30092c181e0371ff79c177bbe952","tid":2364741,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjmcQcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjmcQcc.jpg&h=9a9547d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"079d3c7375f6c6459ff38bd96bd5ccd531f508d4","tid":2364741,"uid":96854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"屌咩,&nbsp;27年升88%，駛撚佢講"},{"pid":"257a43e5eeab9f4052003eba9350c355197cb020","tid":2364741,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"079d3c7375f6c6459ff38bd96bd5ccd531f508d4","tid":2364741,"uid":96854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"屌咩,&nbsp;27年升88%，駛撚佢講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"27年先 88%。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset